description: Alain Cocq's decision to eat again comes after Facebook blocked him from livestreaming his own death.
title: Frenchman Alain Cocq accepts palliative care after bid to livestream death
title_page: Frenchman Alain Cocq accepts palliative care after bid to livestream death - BBC News
maintext: Mr Cocq suffers from a degenerative disease, which causes the walls of his arteries to stick together. He says he has been in a "terminal phase" for more than 30 years.
